00:30:08,530 --> 00:30:10,670
<i>aku dan Kim Dan berusaha dibunuh.</i>

518
00:30:12,130 --> 00:30:13,940
<i>Oleh So In, anak ini adalah...</i>

519
00:30:14,140 --> 00:30:16,410
<i>Kotak Pandora.</i>

520
00:30:17,270 --> 00:30:18,410
<i>Tapi...</i>

521
00:30:18,710 --> 00:30:22,780
<i>Gadis itu kemungkinan Kim Dan.</i>

522
00:30:23,580 --> 00:30:25,250
<i>Ada kematian massal.</i>

523
00:30:25,250 --> 00:30:27,520
<i>Kecuali orang-orang ini.</i>
